quran[18]{c,v,t,f}:
  37,136,"Kaneko ni twajonasile ŵaneo."
  37,137,"Soni chisimu ŵanganyammwe nkwapitaga ŵanganyao (misi jao) kundaŵi."
  37,138,"Ni chilo chakwe, ana ŵangali lunda?"
  40,79,"Allah ni Ajula jwam’bichile jenumanja ilango kuti ine mu yalakweyo nyyikweleje, ni kuti ine muyalakweyo nyyilyeje."
  40,80,"Soni nkwete jenumanja mu yalakweyo ikamuchisyo (yaijinji mpela kuikama nkaka), nambo soni kupitila mu yalakweyo nkombolecheje kuyiyika isako yaili m’mitima mwenu (mpela kutwichilila misigo jenu), nambo soni pa yalakweyo kwisa soni pa yombo nkasanyakulidwaga."
  40,81,"Ni akunnosyaga (Allah) ilosyo Yakwe (yakulosya ukombosi Wakwe). Ana niyapi mu ilosyo ya Allah yankuikana?"
  42,43,"Nambo chisimu jwaapilile, ni kululuka, chisimu yalakweyo ni yaili kwene mu ichindu yakusosekwa kuŵichila ntima."
  42,44,"Sano jwaakunnechelela Allah kusokonechela, basi nganakola nkun’gosa panyuma pakwe. Ni tinchaona ŵalupuso ndema jatachiiona ilagasyo achitiji: “Ana pana litala lyakuujila (ku duniya)?”"
  42,45,"Ni tinchaona ŵanganyao ali nkupelechedwa ku walakwe (Motowo), ali ateteŵele ligongo lya kunyosyeka, ali nkulola ni liso lyakusisa (chamunjenje meso). Sano aŵala ŵaŵakulupilile tachiti: “Chisimu ŵakwasika ni aŵala ŵaalijasikasyisye (Mbepo) achimisyene kwisa soni maŵasa gao (lelo) lisiku lya Kiyama (ligongo lya itendo yao yangalumbana yaŵaliji nkutenda ku duniya), manyililani yanti; chisimu ŵalupuso taŵe mu ilagasyo yakwendelechela.”"
  43,25,"Basi ni twapele ipotesi ŵanganyao. Basi nnole mujaŵelele mbesi ja akukanila!"
  43,26,"Soni (kumbuchilani) katema kajwaŵechete Ibrahima kwa babagwe ni ŵandu ŵakwe kuti: “Chisimu une ndalikangene nayo yankuigalagatila jenumanja.”"
  43,27,"“Ikaŵeje Ajula (Allah) juŵangumbile, basi chisimu Jwalakwe tanjongole.”"
  44,10,"Basi lijembecheyani lisiku lyalichiyika liwunde ni lyosi lyakuloleka."
  44,11,"Lyalichawunichila ŵandu, (ni tachiti): “Ayi ni ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope.”"
  44,12,"“Ambuje ŵetu! Tukungunukulilani ilagasyo, chisimu uwwe chituŵe ŵakulupilila.”"
  45,1,"Hâ. Mîm. ",1:[Asi harufusi ni chimpepe mu isimosimo ya Qur’an. Ni pangali jwine jwaakumanyilila mate gakwe ikaŵeje Allah pe basi.]
  45,2,"Kutulusyidwa kwa Chitabu (Qur’an) kukuumila kwa Allah, Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwalunda lwakusokoka."
  45,3,"Chisimu kumawunde ni petaka kwana ilosyo kwa ŵandu ŵakulupilila (yakulosya kuti Allah apali)."